snippet.title: Jrago II Guardians of Eden - Teaser
snippet.description:
Jrago is back in action with a new multiplayer adventure!

Jrago II Guardians of Eden is an indie Co-Op METROIDVANIA style 2D Platforming Action-Adventure Role Playing Game.
The world is overcome in darkness, and Jrago with his fellow guardians are on an adventure to slay the demons and bring back the light!

Featuring an original soundtrack by "Jrago" the band of the same name, and a whole host of unlockable weapons, armor, magic spells, and more!
This direct sequel to Jrago The Demon Hunter features updated graphics, new abilities, new spells, and multiplayer CO-OP!

This is the second game developed by Jrago Studios, a solo indie developer based in USA.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2704580/Jrago_II_Guardians_of_Eden/
